'''[[Riva]]'s building''' was a structure in the capital city of [[Thani]] on [[Telos IV]]. The building was maintained by Riva, and rented out by [[Denetrus]].

The building's exterior was painted mismatching colors by Denetrus at the command of Riva, who could not decide on a color she liked.

